# Gitavale — Windsurf Rules

## Project
Next.js 14 SaaS that turns GitHub repos into LLM-ready digests.

## Skills
Read `.agents/skills/gitavale/SKILL.md` for full docs: API endpoints, DB schema, env vars, CLI usage.

## Stack
- Framework: Next.js 14 (App Router)
- DB: Prisma + PostgreSQL (Neon)
- Auth: NextAuth.js (`lib/auth.ts`)
- Payments: Polar.sh (`lib/polar.ts`)
- API Auth: Bearer tokens (`gta_` prefix) hashed SHA-256 in DB
- CLI: Python (`cli-anything-gitavale/`)

## Conventions
- Server components: use `getServerSession(authOptions)`
- New Prisma fields: cast `as any` locally (postinstall runs `prisma db push` on Vercel)
- CSS utilities: `glass-panel`, `glass-card`, `btn-primary`, `btn-glass` from `globals.css`
- Deploy: push to GitHub → Vercel auto-deploys
